column5: Anyone had a look lately? Is it still frozen or open? Just wondering how long before we can give it a try?
I'd hazard a guess it's a little cold still
I'd hazard a guess it's a little cold still I had a moment of weakness, I need to get out on the water and catch a fish....
The channels will not wake up till 55 degrees most times.   Art
Probably a few weeks away depending on the weather of course..
